>YAW-330B</td><td>SET</td><td>1</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Dual cell atmospheric consistometer</td><td>TG-1220C</td><td>SET</td><td>2</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Mud Cells</td><td>Standard</td><td>SET</td><td>4</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Settlement Meter</td><td>Standard</td><td>SET</td><td>1</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>High Pressure Compressor</td><td>HET-80</td><td>SET</td><td>2</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Gas Migration Analyzer</td><td>TG-4268</td><td>SET</td><td>1</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Dynamic press filter ht/hp</td><td>TG-1720</td><td>SET</td><td>1</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Grout expansion and shrinkage meter</td><td>TG-4268</td><td>SET</td><td>1</td></tr>\r\n\r\n</tbody></table>', 'Servicio_Cementacion.png', 'We provide Primary and Secondary Cementing services in Oil and Gas Wells, Well Abandonment, Fluid Displacement, Training Integrity Tests (PIP), Grava Packaging.', 'Carrusel_Cementacion.png'),
(40, 'Ingles', 'SERVICIO', 'Coiled Tubing', '<h3 class="my-4" align="justify"><span class="text-danger fa fa-cog fa-spin"></span> PREVIOUS EXPERIENCES:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:" arial","sans-serif""="">Development of more than 250 jobs in the last 5 years in the operational areas of the Oil Belt of the Orinoco and North of Monagas.</span></span></li><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:" arial","sans-serif";="" color:black;mso-themecolor:text1"="">These services include Stimulation, Cleaning, Induction, Fluid Pumping, Fishing, among others.</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:" arial","sans-serif""="">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class="my-4" align="justify"><span class="text-danger fa fa-cog fa-spin"></span> AVAILABLE SERVICES:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:" arial","sans-serif""="">Currently we have a continuous Piping Unit with which we can perform services of:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div align="justify">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Fishing with Coiled Tubing.</li>\r\n<li>Discharge of acidified well residual liquid.</li>\r\n<li>Cleaning and removal of fillings.</li>\r\n<li>Acidification with Coiled Tubing.</li>\r\n<li>Wax removal from horizontal well.</li>\r\n<li>Kill accident well.</li>\r\n<li>Sand removal with Coiled Tubing.</li>\r\n<li>Gas lift with Coiled Tubing.</li>\r\n<li>Blowing well displacement.</li>\r\n<li>Gas well cleaning.</li>\r\n<li>Gas well insulation and discharge relief.</li>\r\n<li>Evaluation of wells and inductions without nitrogen.</li>\r\n<li>Chemical cleanings.</li>\r\n<li>Nitrogen induction.</li>\r\n<li>Cleaning with nitrified fluids.</li>\r\n<li>Reactive stimulations (Acids).</li>\r\n<li>Non-reactive stimulations (Solvents and surfactants).</li>\r\n<li>Cementation (Tapons and Forzations).</li>\r\n<li>Cleaning with High Impact Jet (High Pressure).</li>\r\n<li>Drilling/milling application.</li>\r\n<li>Lower CT completion.</li>\r\n<li>Pressure and temperature registers in memory mode. Well canyoning.</li>\r\n\r\n</ul></div>', 'Servicio_Coiled_Tubing.png', 'Fishing Services, Stimulation, Isolation and Discharge Aid, Nitrogen Induction, Cementation and Canyoning, Pressure and Temperature Records.', 'Carrusel_Coiled_Tubing.png'),
(41, 'Ingles', 'SERVICIO', 'Well Testing', '<h3 class="my-4" align="justify"><span class="text-danger fa fa-cog fa-spin"></span> AVAILABLE SERVICES:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span lang="ES-TRAD">We have five teams with which we can perform services of:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span lang="ES-TRAD"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><b><span lang="ES-TRAD">A.- TESTS TO DETERMINE FUND PRESS AND PRODUCTIVE CAPACITY:</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Back Pressure Test.</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Isochronous or Isocrona Test.</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Modified Isochronous Test.</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Inverse productivity index.</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Modified Productivity Index Test.</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span lang="ES-TRAD">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><b><span lang="ES-TRAD">B.- TESTS TO DETERMINE THE PARAMETERS OF THE RESERVOIR:</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Drawdown Test.</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Multirate Test (Multiflujo).</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">2 Rates Test.</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Builtup Test. (Press Restoration).</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Method of the Type curve.</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Servicio_Well_Testing.png', 'We test Back Pressure, Isocronal, Productivity index and Modified, Drawdown, Multirate, 2 Rates, Builtup, and Type Curve Method.', 'Carrusel_Well_Testing.png'),
(42, 'Ingles', 'SERVICIO', 'Wireline', '<h3 class="my-4" align="justify"><span class="text-danger fa fa-cog fa-spin"></span> Available Services:</h3>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span lang="ES-TRAD">Currently we have a team with which we can perform services of:</span></p>\r\n<div align="justify"><ul><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Pipeline Check.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Mechanical check.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Zone Change.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Cleaning: Removal of paraffins, sand and scale through the use of cutters, brushes, sand pumps or hydrostatic or acid pumps.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Redesign of valves for artificial gas lift and/or blind valves.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Temperature (BHT) and Background Pressure (BHP) Recording Take: With elements of 0-600 oF and 0-10000 psi.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Placement of test tool or stopper for packing settlement.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Opening and closing of shirts for verification of the settlement of the packings.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Tool Fishing and Guayas: Using fine guaya.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Single Shot and Multi Shot Fishing: In directional registers.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Fishing for Detonador Strips.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Fishing surface valves and safety caps.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Open pit profiling:</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Induction</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Spontaneous Potential</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Gamma Ray</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Resistivity</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Density – Neutron.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Sonic.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Caliper.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Well-to-hole drilling:</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Plt.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">CBL - VDL Cementing Records.</span></li><li><span lang="ES-TRAD">Cannonwork.</span></li></ul></div>', 'Servicio_Guaya_Fina_Electrica.png', 'Pipeline Check, Mechanical, Zone Change, Cleaning, Valve Redesign, BHT/BHP, Test Tool Placement, Opening and Closing of Shirts and Fishing.', 'Carrusel_Guaya_Fina_Electrica.png'),
